name: Car-find
tagline: Windows Phone 8 App - Application to help the user locate their parked vehicle.
body:
### Welcome to LC Points.
LC Points - Is a Windows Universal application that calculates Irish Leaving Certificate points, based on subject/grade combinations entered. 

[Download on Windows Store](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/apps/car-find/9wzdncrdcds0)

### Demo


[Demo ](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kNvesU4nZRw)
